	[em 
		"The World's Hardest Game
	]em
	". The game is simple: move a square from one end of a level to the other without being touched by enemy circles. Make contact with an enemy circle and you must do the whole level all over again. In a number of levels, you are also required to collect yellow circles that are needed to complete the level. New in this sequel are keys that unlock doors when collected.
